# Welcome to the WDI Guide

This website provides a comprehensive guide to indicator selection for the World Development Indicators (WDI).

## Overview

The World Development Indicators (WDI) are a key resource for policymakers, researchers, and the public, offering a reliable collection of development data. Use the navigation bar to explore sections such as the indicator framework, metrics, and evaluation criteria.

